{"tid":2415670,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黃店食肆「火鍋撚」旺角分店被指非法擴展營業範圍暫時吊銷牌照14天","createTime":"2021-02-20T12:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T08:23:59.000Z","uid":78519,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6c13122495ab3866b84c44896ca3a254ecc5fbc0","tid":2415670,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:15:37.000Z","msg":"黃店食肆「火鍋撚」旺角分店被食環署指非法擴展營業範圍，因屢次違反《食物業規例》，被暫時吊銷牌照14天。<br />\n<br />\n「火鍋撚」在facebook專頁稱，旺角分店內部裝修，2月20日至3月5日暫停營業，中環及西環分店則正常營業。<br />\n<br />\n荃灣「天祥餐廳小廚」同遭釘牌14日<br />\n<br />\n另外，荃灣青龍頭村2號地下「天祥餐廳小廚」同樣因非法擴展營業範圍，屢次違反《食物業規例》，被食環署暫時吊銷牌照14天，由今日至3月5日須暫停營業。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210220/NDDJ2WQT2ZGABM6JIQKCMNVHDI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210220%2FNDDJ2WQT2ZGABM6JIQKCMNVHDI%2F&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkqpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=a4738c0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210220%2FNDDJ2WQT2ZGABM6JIQKCMNVHDI%2F&h=78778d32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210220/NDDJ2WQT2ZGABM6JIQKCMNVHDI/</a>"},{"pid":"092c8f118b082e4330e02772460aa1157060d262","tid":2415670,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:53:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a346bb9d91c8e68c2d8535a4bd7615d2e1d2c0","tid":2415670,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:01:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c3cf94b3efd34f4ab391cfb85afa0d3aa26cd6","tid":2415670,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T02:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"238d68326a073f4bf3b8fe37f2d9146d3d08bc3d","tid":2415670,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02